title: i have a secret…..
itunes:title: i have a secret…..
description:
Brooke and Danielle are REVEALING YOUR SECRETS….  The gals asked you all on Instagram to share your juiciest ones about life, love and everything in between.  Brooke and Danielle are blindly reacting to these confessions and some are SHOCKING to say the least!  The gals also catch you up on their weekends, and Danielle shares a story about how she has truly become a local at the comedy club.  Be sure to follow and tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies/stories!
